### PIPELINE-API-001 | 분석 단계 상태 조회
### Markdown source: docs/03_API/PHASE2_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: GET /api/pipeline/{job_id}/stages
### 관련 기능 ID: PROJECT-PIPELINE-B-201, PROJECT-PIPELINE-F-201,
### PROJECT-PIPELINE-F-301
### 상태: 시작 전 (Phase 2)
### 변경 이력: PROJECT-PIPELINE-API-001 Notion 초안의 /status 단일 상태를
### PIPELINE-API-001 단계별 /stages 응답으로 고도화.
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@jobId = a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pipeline/{{jobId}}/stages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 200 OK
### {
###   "code": 200, "message": "success",
###   "data": {
###     "jobId": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890", "overallStatus": "running",
###     "stages": [
###       {"name":"clone","status":"completed","startedAt":"2026-06-18T10:00:00Z","completedAt":"2026-06-18T10:00:30Z","elapsedSeconds":30.5},
###       {"name":"parse","status":"completed","startedAt":"2026-06-18T10:00:31Z","completedAt":"2026-06-18T10:01:00Z","elapsedSeconds":29.0},
###       {"name":"embed","status":"running","startedAt":"2026-06-18T10:01:01Z","completedAt":null,"elapsedSeconds":null},
###       {"name":"agent","status":"queued","startedAt":null,"completedAt":null,"elapsedSeconds":null},
###       {"name":"docs","status":"queued","startedAt":null,"completedAt":null,"elapsedSeconds":null}
###     ]
###   }
### }
### overallStatus/stages[].status: queued | running | completed | failed
### stages[].name: clone | parse | embed | agent | docs

### [오류] 존재하지 않는 job
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pipeline/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/stages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 401 UNAUTHORIZED / 404 JOB_NOT_FOUND
### {"code":404,"message":"분석 작업을 찾을 수 없습니다.","data":null,"error":{"code":"JOB_NOT_FOUND","detail":null,"field":"jobId","retryable":false}}
